These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, reading, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, july, august
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, trike
City: hamburg, prague, venice
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the motorbike##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person driving the trike and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in july is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the bus##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Hobby         | reading    | skydiving  | hiking        |
| Birthday           | december | july   | august      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Transport   | motorbike     | bus  | trike       |
| City         | hamburg     | prague | venice |

