.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
House: art-deco, ranch-style, craftsman
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: metal, punk, rock
3 different games are played: canasta, whist, go
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, august, september
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's birthday is in september is the person playing whist##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in september is the craftsman house##1
 3. the craftsman house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the person playing go is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the fan of metal##1
 7. the fan of punk is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the art-deco house##1
 9. the craftsman house is on the right of the fan of rock##1
10. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| House   | art-deco  | craftsman  | ranch-style     |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | punk      | metal         |
| Game   | go      | whist   | canasta    |
| Birthday           | july        | september      | august         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

