There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, russian
3 different pets are kept: hamster, hedgehog, mouse
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, june, august
 1. the freelancer is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 2. the russian is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the nurse##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the owner of the hedgehog##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the indian and the townhouse house##2
 8. the indian is on the left of the victorian house##1
 9. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the freelancer##1
11. the indian is the nurse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
