.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, milk, soy-milk
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, fishing, sudoku
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, security-guard, social-worker
There are 3 different favourite colors: azure, yellow, black
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, jazz, pop
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, amaryllis, dahlia
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, chaman, bolivar
 1. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who growsdahlia##1
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who likes black##1
 4. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
 5. the fan of country is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking almond-milk##2
 6. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the musician is the bolivar-smoker##1
 9. the person drinking milk is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | milk           | soy-milk      |
| Hobby         | chess       | sudoku         | fishing       |
| Job           | musician    | security-guard | social-worker |
| Color   | azure       | black         | yellow      |
| Music-Genre   | pop         | country        | jazz          |
| Flower   | dahlia   | amaryllis       | orchid         |
| Cigar           | bolivar       | dannemann         | chaman        |

