3 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: lacrosse, swimming, weightlifting
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, bellflower, amaryllis
 1. the person eating onion is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 2. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the owner of the horse##1
 3. the game-smoker is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 4. the montecristo-smoker is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is swimming and the fan of pop##2
 6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is between the person who's sport is lacrosse and the owner of the snake##2
 7. the person who growszinnia is between the person eating strawberry and the pall-mall-smoker##2
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of indie##1
 9. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the fan of indie##1
10. the person watching animation movies is the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2       |     3      |
| Cigar      | pall-mall          | game         | montecristo      |
