3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, guinea-pig
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, soccer, water-polo
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, strawberry, pepper
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the cain-smoker##1
 4. the pall-mall-smoker is the person watching disaster movies##1
 5. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 7. the person eating pepper is between the person traveling to new-york and the american##2
 8. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating raspberry##1
10. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
11. the person eating raspberry is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| City      | new-york | hamburg      | paris      |
| Cigar         | cain     | baccarat     | pall-mall  |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | adventure  | disaster |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| Pet           | bird        | guinea-pig | fish     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Food     | strawberry        | pepper        | raspberry   |

