.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: october, may, march
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bluemaster, dannemann
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, indie, funk
1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the fan of funk is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the blend-smoker##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the bluemaster-smoker##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the dannemann-smoker and the person who's birthday is in march##2
6. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
8. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | juice      | milk       |
| Food          | mango      | pumpkin    | broccoli   |
| Birthday         | march    | october     | may     |
| Cigar           | bluemaster    | blend | dannemann   |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | mystery    | epic       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Music-Genre     | indie       | r&b | funk |

