There 3 different types of food: lettuce, peach, zucchini
3 different pets are kept: dog, bird, lizard
3 different games are played: scrabble, go, canasta
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
City: venice, boston, prague
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, scooter, ship
1. the person driving the scooter is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
4. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
5. the person eating peach is between the person drinking fanta and the owner of the dog##2
6. the person eating zucchini is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the person driving the motorbike is the person playing canasta##1
9. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Beverage      | fanta       | coffee     | cola         |
| Food          | lettuce     | peach      | zucchini     |
| Pet         | bird | lizard    | dog      |
| Game   | scrabble   | go | canasta    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| City         | venice     | boston | prague |
| Transport     | scooter     | ship       | motorbike    |

