.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, dancing, cooking
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, spinach, zucchini
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, orchid, rose
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, spy, disaster
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, basketball, cycling
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person who's sport is baseball##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who's hobby is cooking and the person watching disaster movies##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person who's sport is cycling##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the person who growsorchid is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
9. the french is between the person eating broccoli and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby      | dancing    | traveling       | cooking      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Flower           | orchid  | amaryllis | rose    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Movie-Genre           | disaster     | drama        | spy |
| Sport         | basketball | baseball   | cycling  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 